OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,FJohn Swinney has said he "cannot wait"
OL,8,Ffor the 2026 Commonwealth Games to get
OL,9,Funder way, adding that the Glasgow
OL,10,Ftournament would "showcase Scotland's
OL,11,Flove of sport to the world".
OL,13,FThe Scottish First Minister spoke out
OL,14,Fat the start of the King's Baton
OL,15,FRelay, which acts as a curtain-raiser
OL,16,Ffor the sporting contest.
OL,26,@oD@ZOUoD@fO]rD@ROUsD@[O]
