OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,FForm Wednesday July 1, the baton will
OL,8,Ftravel from the Team Scotland camp in
OL,9,FGlasgow to more than 50 events across
OL,10,Fthe country, celebrating Scottish
OL,11,Fsport, culture, the Commonwealth and
OL,12,Fthe Games themselves.
OL,14,FWith the sporting contest due to take
OL,15,Fplace in Glasgow from July 23 to
OL,16,FAugust 2, Mr Swinney said it would be
OL,17,Fpart of a "summer of sport" for
OL,18,FScotland.
OL,26,@yD@KOUyD@[O]
