OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,FA slimmed-down version of the
OL,8,Ftournament will see athletes compete
OL,9,Fin 10 sports ` with Glasgow hosting
OL,10,Fthe event after the Australian state
OL,11,Fof Victoria withdrew amid concerns
OL,12,Fover costs.
OL,14,FMr Swinney, however, has previously
OL,15,Fmade clear there will be "no call on
OL,16,Fthe public purse" as a result of the
OL,17,FGames coming to Glasgow for the second
OL,18,Ftime in 12 years, with the city having
OL,19,Fpreviously hosted the contest in 2014.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@QO]
