OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,FBut the Scottish Government is
OL,8,Fproviding #20 million for a series of
OL,9,Ffree and low-cost sporting activities
OL,10,Ffor youngsters over the summer ` with
OL,11,Fministers also investing #245,000 to
OL,12,Fsupport more than 50 free events
OL,13,Fduring the Scottish leg of the King's
OL,14,FBaton Relay.
OL,16,FSpeaking ahead of the start of the
OL,17,Frelay, Mr Swinney said: "The Glasgow
OL,18,F2026 Commonwealth Games will showcase
OL,19,FScotland's love of sport to the world
OL,20,F` and I cannot wait."
OL,26,@yD@YOU|D@UO]
