OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,FWith Scottish football fans having
OL,8,F"captured the hearts of millions" when
OL,9,Fthey followed the national team in the
OL,10,FWorld Cup finals, the First Minister
OL,11,Fadded that the Glasgow 2026 Games
OL,12,Fwould be "an exciting opportunity to
OL,13,Fbuild on our global brand and show the
OL,14,Fworld what a fantastic place Scotland
OL,15,Fis to live, work, study and do
OL,16,Fbusiness in, and to visit".
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@aO]tD@JOUxD@ZO]
