OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,FHe stated: "We want the legacy of this
OL,8,Fsummer of sport ` the 2026 Fifa World
OL,9,FCup, Glasgow 2026 and the women's
OL,10,Fhockey and cricket team world cup
OL,11,Fcampaigns ` to stretch far beyond the
OL,12,Fnext few months.
OL,14,F"Our #20 million summer of sport
OL,15,Ffunding will create free sporting
OL,16,Fopportunities for thousands of young
OL,17,Fpeople, encouraging a new generation
OL,18,Fto enjoy taking part in physical
OL,19,Factivity.
OL,26,@oD@LOUvD@AOU
