OL,3,CGlasgow Games will 'showcase
OL,4,CScotland's love of sport', John
OL,5,CSwinney says
OL,7,F"The King's Baton Relay will carry the
OL,8,Fexcitement of the Commonwealth Games
OL,9,Fto every corner of Scotland.
OL,11,F"We are supporting free events across
OL,12,Fthe country to mark this and I want
OL,13,Feveryone to come along, get active and
OL,14,Fbe part of something truly special."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUvD@dO]
